{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessLauncherProtocol"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessLauncherProtocol\/takeStdout(fd:)"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"takeStdout","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"fd","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO26SubprocessLauncherProtocolPAAE10takeStdout2fdySi_tF","title":"takeStdout(fd:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GIO"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"takeStdout","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"fd","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fd"},{"type":"text","text":" is -1 then any previously given fd is unset."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that the default behaviour is to pass stdout through to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stdout of the parent process."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The passed "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fd"},{"text":" is noted but will not be touched in the current","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"process.  It is therefore necessary that it be kept open by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"caller until the subprocess is spawned.  The file descriptor will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"also not be explicitly closed on the child side, so it must be marked","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"O_CLOEXEC if that’s what you want.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You may not set a stdout fd if a stdout file path is already set or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if the launcher flags contain any flags directing stdout elsewhere."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This feature is only available on UNIX."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the file descriptor to use as the stdout for spawned processes.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/subprocesslauncherprotocol\/takestdout(fd:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SubprocessLauncherProtocol/takeStdout(fd:)":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/subprocesslauncherprotocol\/takestdout(fd:)","abstract":[{"text":"Sets the file descriptor to use as the stdout for spawned processes.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessLauncherProtocol\/takeStdout(fd:)","title":"takeStdout(fd:)","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"takeStdout","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"fd","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SubprocessLauncherProtocol":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifi